ing wizards: my recommendations (long)</span><hr size=1> IMO, Wizards are perfect on the dmg table wise. We dont need any increases there. Where we need something is in the utility spell section to make us more profitable to a group. Damage is all good,but lots of class can provide dmg to some point as well as other nice abilities. A mage can do decent dmg, but can also CoH peoples around etc.<br>
